supportDesc.extent: 120 leaves : 208 x 150 (180 x 125) mm. bound to 212 x 152 mm
supportDesc.foliation: Paper, 120; [ii], 1-87, [88-118]; contemporary foliation in ink, modern foliation in pentil, upper right recto.

layoutDesc.layout: Written in 22 long lines; ruled in lead.

scriptDesc.scriptNote: Written in an italic script by Domnus Severinus (f. 81v, 117v), with commentary in a small hand. Notes in red ink refer to Severinus in the 3rd person (f. 61v, 62v, 66r).

origin.p: Written in Bologna ca. 1592 (inscription, f. i recto).
